<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
#myBtn {
    position: absolute;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<p>A function is triggered when the user move mouse on the button field.</p>

<button type="button" id="myBtn" onmouseover="myFunction()" onmouseout="myFunction2()">Set left position to 100 px</button>

<script>
function myFunction() {
    document.getElementById("myBtn").style.left = "600px";
}

function myFunction2() {
   document.getElementById("myBtn").style.left = "10px";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
